Class Summary
ActivityHelper Helper activity used for triggering the Intent recognition, and for collecting the results.
ServiceHelper Service helper that connects the IME with the activity that triggers the recognition and that will receive the recognition result.
VoiceRecognitionTrigger Triggers a voice recognition by using ImeTrigger or IntentApiTrigger.
